<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_424_r1l2"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dinſt cʒeuoꝛ / Als Jr
                        vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Jüten Maẏrin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_424_r1l3">der Judin <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> /
